{"id":21,"parent_id":0,"book_id":0,"content_id":1,"language_id":0,"display_order":21,"title":"The New Adventures of Matt and Mandy","subtitle":"","short_title":"The New Adventures of Matt and Mandy","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"article","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.head1"},[".title","The New Adventures of Matt & Mandy"]],[".bodyBlock",[".figure",{"id":"f1","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f1"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/leaders/fr13jul30-matt-and-mandy.jpg"}],[".credit",["p.para",{"id":"p2","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p2"},"Illustrations by Maryn Roos"]],["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p3"},"Saturday morning at the Cooper house"]],[".figure",{"id":"f2","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f2"},["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p4"},"Don’t tell me Matt and Dad are still sleeping. I thought I was the lazy one on Saturdays."],["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p5"},"Oh, they’ve already had breakfast and left. They went to see Matt’s new friend, Franco."]],[".figure",{"id":"f3","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f3"},["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p6"},"He has a new friend already? That’s not fair. I haven’t found any new friends yet. I wish we hadn’t moved!"],["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p7"},"We’ve only been here a week. Just give it time. You made lots of friends at your old school. You’ll make friends here too."]],[".figure",{"id":"f4","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f4"},["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p8"},"Remember, if you want to have a friend …"],["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p9"},"I know, I know. If you want to have a friend, be a friend."]],[".figure",{"id":"f5","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f5"},["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p10"},"Meanwhile, at Franco’s house …"],["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p11"},"Hi, I’m Josh Cooper."],["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p12"},"I’m Hector Delgado."]],[".figure",{"id":"f6","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f6"},["p.para",{"id":"p13","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p13"},"Some of these rocks are really cool. What’s this one?"],["p.para",{"id":"p14","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p14"},"That’s a geode. Lots of them are hollow, and some have awesome crystals inside. My dad says geodes are like some people—not much to look at on the outside, but pretty cool inside."]],[".figure",{"id":"f7","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f7"},["p.para",{"id":"p15","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p15"},"If they’re like people, are any of these rocks musical?"],["p.para",{"id":"p16","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p16"},"What do you mean?"]],[".figure",{"id":"f8","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f8"},["p.para",{"id":"p17","uri":"/friend/2013/07/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p17"},"Because then we could have a rock concert!"]]]]]],"refs":null}
